      <title outputclass="H4ForH3_1_9" class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">32.502-2</ph> Contract finance office clearance.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p otherprops="Body" outputclass="Body" class="- topic/p ">The contracting officer shall obtain the approval of the contract finance office or other offices designated under agency procedures before taking any of the following actions:</p>
         <ol class="- topic/ol " id="d2089e16">
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d2103e20" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  Providing a progress payment rate higher than the customary rate (see <xref href="FAR-i1082067.dita#i1082067"
                        base="i1082067"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.501-1</xref>).</p>
            </li>
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d2103e32" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  Deviating from the progress payments terms prescribed in this part.</p>
            </li>
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d2103e41" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  Providing progress payments to a contractor-</p>
               <ol class="- topic/ol " id="d2089e47">
                  <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d2103e51" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        Whose financial condition is in doubt;</p>
                  </li>
                  <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d2103e60" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        Who has had an advance payment request or loan guarantee denied for financial reasons (or approved but withdrawn or lapsed) within the previous 12 months; or</p>
                  </li>
                  <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d2103e69" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        Who is named in the consolidated list of contractors indebted to the United States (known commonly as the “Hold-up List”).</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
